---
---

<div class="about-page" data-about-page>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="hero-dark" data-reveal>
    <span class="hero-dark-eyebrow">About</span>
    <h1 class="hero-dark-name">Thor G. Draper Jr</h1>
    <p class="hero-dark-role">Non-traditional operator, builder, teacher, and writer.</p>
    <p class="ab-hero-note">
      This blog is my drafting ground and working library -- a place to test ideas, document principles, and leave a clearer record of how I think and where I am headed.
    </p>
    <p class="ab-hero-scope">
      Current chapter: Senior Security Solution Engineer at Microsoft, working where cloud security, AI, and real-world execution meet.
    </p>
  </header>

  <!-- The Thread -->
  <section class="ab-thread ab-section-surface" data-reveal>
    <h2 class="ab-section-title">The Non-Traditional Path Is the Point</h2>
    <p class="ab-lead">
      I sold gym memberships, managed a rental car fleet, ran my own business, taught cybersecurity to career-changers, and now I architect security solutions for healthcare's most critical clouds. None of that was accidental.
    </p>
    <p class="ab-body">
      A decade in sales and management taught me to read rooms, build trust fast, and translate complexity into action. Entrepreneurship taught me to own outcomes when nobody else is coming to fix it. Teaching sharpened the ability to break down hard problems for any audience. Every chapter was a deliberate bet that paid compound interest into the next one.
    </p>
    <div class="ab-thread-cta">
      <a href="/resume/" class="button-ghost">See the full career timeline</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Drives Me -->
  <section class="ab-drive ab-section-surface">
    <h2 class="ab-section-title" data-reveal>What Drives Me</h2>
    <div class="ab-drive-grid">
      <div class="ab-callout" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <span class="ab-callout-label">Word of the Year</span>
        <span class="ab-callout-value">Velocity</span>
        <p class="ab-callout-desc">
          Every morning starts with a journal entry under this word. It is not about speed for its own sake -- it is about sharpening focus, cutting drag, and keeping momentum toward the work that matters most.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-drive-items">
        <div class="ab-drive-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
          <h3 class="ab-drive-item-title">Technology Change With Consequence</h3>
          <p>I care most about the moments when new technology stops being a novelty and starts changing how teams operate, decide, and take responsibility.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="ab-drive-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
          <h3 class="ab-drive-item-title">Enablement as Force Multiplier</h3>
          <p>The best work scales through other people. I build playbooks, workshops, and hands-on labs that help teams move faster without losing clarity.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Beyond the Keyboard -->
  <section class="ab-personal ab-section-surface">
    <h2 class="ab-section-title" data-reveal>Beyond the Keyboard</h2>
    <div class="ab-personal-grid">
      <div class="ab-personal-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="1">
        <svg class="ab-personal-icon" aria-hidden="true" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 2.83l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-4 0v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83-2.83l.06-.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.68 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1 0-4h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83-2.83l.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 4.68a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 4 0v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 2.83l-.06.06A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 19.4 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 0 4h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"/></svg>
        <p>Experimenting with AI tools and automation to eliminate the repetitive and make room for the meaningful</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-personal-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="2">
        <svg class="ab-personal-icon" aria-hidden="true" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 8h1a4 4 0 0 1 0 8h-1"/><path d="M2 8h16v9a4 4 0 0 1-4 4H6a4 4 0 0 1-4-4V8z"/><line x1="6" y1="1" x2="6" y2="4"/><line x1="10" y1="1" x2="10" y2="4"/><line x1="14" y1="1" x2="14" y2="4"/></svg>
        <p>Road-trip cafe hunter -- Jaspers' Ottos Cache remains the gold standard</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-personal-item" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="3">
        <svg class="ab-personal-icon" aria-hidden="true" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
        <p>Daily journaling habit and strategic financial planning to fuel future chapters</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Connect -->
  <section class="ab-connect ab-section-surface" data-reveal>
    <h2 class="ab-section-title">Let's Connect</h2>
    <p class="ab-connect-text">
      I am always open to conversations about technology strategy, AI, enablement, non-traditional career paths, or what makes a great cafe worth the detour.
    </p>
    <div class="ab-connect-actions">
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/thor-draper-jr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="button-ghost ab-cta-primary">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="/resume/" class="button-ghost">View the Resume</a>
      <a href="/archive/" class="button-ghost">Browse the Archive</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>
